						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://www.bcgs.ca/?p=6669" title="3:23 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2016-08-07T15:23:31+00:00" pubdate>August 7, 2016</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.bcgs.ca/?author=3" title="View all posts by DRogers" rel="author">DRogers</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
						<div class="comments-link">
				<a href="http://www.bcgs.ca/?p=6669#respond"><span class="leave-reply">Reply</span></a>			</div>
