Birmingham, England. 

April 7-9, 2016 - Who Do You Think You Are
NEC, Birmingham, England.  
See 2016 slides and handouts WDYTYA Live Speakers&#039; Handouts Some handouts from the  past are also available on-line free and some sessions may be on YouTube. 
The DNA related sessions sponsored by FamilyTreeDNA and organized by ISOGG will be on YouTube soon. Go to BCGS Group Update - April 2016 for links.

